170
00:14:15,022 --> 00:14:16,481
Hard to explain.

171
00:14:21,945 --> 00:14:26,199
Remember what the dnc folks told me
two years ago? How to take the statehouse?

172
00:14:26,283 --> 00:14:28,952
Build something downtown
and stick your name on it,

173
00:14:29,036 --> 00:14:32,039
