179
00:14:54,728 --> 00:14:57,689
First of all, I'm surprised
to see so much media here.

180
00:14:57,773 --> 00:15:00,817
A press event held earlier today
to announce the revitalization

181
00:15:00,901 --> 00:15:03,737
